<html>
<big><big><b>Instructions for downloading files</b></big></big>
<p>
<b>Macintosh with Safari web browser</b>:
<ol>
<li>hold down the Control key
<li>click on a file name
<li>choose "Download Linked File" from the menu
</ol>
<p>
<b>Macintosh with Firefox web browser</b>:
<ol>
<li>hold down the Control key
<li>click on a file name
<li>choose "Save Link As" from the menu
</ol>
<p>
<b>Windows with Internet Explorer:</b>
<ol>
<li>click on a file name with the right mouse button
<li>choose "Save Target As" from the menu
</ol>
</html>
